    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>https://gall-ardo.github.io/pt-tr/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://gall-ardo.github.io/pt-tr/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;hakkımda&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  Hakkımda&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#hakk%c4%b1mda&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Merhaba, ben &lt;strong&gt;Halil Arda Özongun&lt;/strong&gt;. &lt;strong&gt;Bilkent Üniversitesi&lt;/strong&gt; Bilgisayar Mühendisliği öğrencisiyim ve şu anda &lt;strong&gt;Erasmus değişim programı&lt;/strong&gt; kapsamında &lt;strong&gt;ISCTE – Instituto Universitário de Lisboa&lt;/strong&gt;’da, Portekiz’de eğitimime devam ediyorum.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Generative deep learning&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;computer vision&lt;/strong&gt; ve &lt;strong&gt;3D vision&lt;/strong&gt; alanlarıyla ilgileniyorum. &lt;a href=&#34;https://web.cs.hacettepe.edu.tr/~erkut/&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Prof. Erkut Erdem&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ve &lt;a href=&#34;https://aykuterdem.github.io&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Prof. Aykut Erdem&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ile diffusion-based modeller üzerine çalışıyorum — &lt;strong&gt;low-light image enhancement&lt;/strong&gt; ve &lt;strong&gt;360° panoramic video generation&lt;/strong&gt; projelerinde yer alıyorum. Daha önce &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.cs.bilkent.edu.tr/~adundar/&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Asst. Prof. Ayşegül Dündar&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ile &lt;strong&gt;DLR Lab&lt;/strong&gt;’da &lt;strong&gt;text-to-video synthesis&lt;/strong&gt; ve temporal consistency üzerine çalıştım.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
